extends layout

block content
  section.guideContent
    nav.nav.pageNav
      ul
        li
          a(href="#fonts") Fonts
        li
          a(href="#headings") Headings
        li
          a(href="#text") Text
    h1.guideHeading Typography
    a(name="fonts")
    h2.guideHeading Font Family
    div.example
      p The font used in this site is "Noto Sans". The font stack should also have the fallback of "sans-serif" in case the primary font does not load.
    pre.codeBlock.
      body {
        font-family: 'Noto Sans', sans-serif;
      }
    h2.guideHeading Formatting
    div.example
      p The base text formatting for the site should be as listed below.
    pre.codeBlock.
      body {
        color: $darkGray;
        font-size: 100%;
        line-height: 1.5em;
      }
    a(name="headings")
    h2.guideHeading Headings
    p Heading tags should be used to define
      strong  importance only
      | . h1 being the most important. Any styling should be done through the use of additional classes. There may be multiple h1 tags on a page, but only one per section or article. Heading tags should
      strong  NOT
      |  be used as a styling tool to achieve a larger font size.
    div.example
      p
        h1 Heading 1
      p
        h2 Heading 2
      p
        h3 Heading 3
    pre.codeBlock.
      &lt;h1&gt;Heading 1&lt;/h1&gt;
      &lt;h2&gt;Heading 2&lt;/h2&gt;
      &lt;h3&gt;Heading 3&lt;/h3&gt;
    a(name="text")
    h2.guideHeading Text
    p Paragraphs should be separated by the &lt;p&gt; tag, there should be no use of a &lt;br&gt; tag to separate text.
    div.example
      p Williamsburg disrupt lomo, church-key PBR&B McSweeney's cred literally banh mi kogi banjo umami mustache meggings. Messenger bag gastropub authentic slow-carb, mlkshk skateboard craft beer Tumblr brunch wayfarers YOLO Portland food truck umami fanny pack.
      p Taxidermy umami 90's pickled craft beer. Mixtape Odd Future pop-up butcher. Next level four dollar toast meh salvia, flexitarian gastropub chambray you probably haven't heard of them ethical Pitchfork forage food truck farm-to-table High Life Brooklyn. Wolf meh salvia biodiesel quinoa forage. Kogi cardigan Tumblr, selvage meditation pug sriracha lo-fi direct trade.&lt;/p&gt;
    pre.codeBlock.
      &lt;p&gt; Williamsburg disrupt lomo, church-key PBR&B McSweeney's cred literally banh mi kogi banjo umami mustache meggings. Messenger bag gastropub authentic slow-carb, mlkshk skateboard craft beer Tumblr brunch wayfarers YOLO Portland food truck umami fanny pack.&lt;/p&gt;
