    h2.guideHeading Bold
    div.example
      p Make something
        strong  stand out.
    pre.codeBlock.
      &lt;p&gt;Make something &lt;strong&gt;stand out.&lt;/strong&gt;
    h2.guideHeading Emphasis
    div.example
      p Give something
        em  emphasis.
    pre.codeBlock.
      &lt;p&gt;Give something &lt;em&gt;emphasis.&lt;/em&gt;
